      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a functional choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows clear signs of age, including some visible cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, as well as minor mechanical items that may need attention soon. It has served well over the years, and with a bit of continued care, it still has life left in it. We encourage any interested buyers to come see it in person to get a full sense of its current state.",
