    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Available now is a reliable sedan in fair condition, perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver and isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small door dings, and the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It has been a steady commuter for years, and while it isn't a showpiece, it remains a solid, functional vehicle for the price.",
