    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, never smoked in, and there isn't a single blemish to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
