      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54 power plant. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and has been meticulously maintained, with a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and valve clearance adjustment recently completed to ensure optimal timing and compression. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and delivered through a limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, having received preventative subframe reinforcement to maintain peak torsional rigidity under lateral load. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss with no evidence of panel misalignment, while the interior remains free of bolster wear or UV degradation. A mechanically synchronized, collector-quality vehicle for the true driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
