    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, mirror-like gloss free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are firm and supple with zero bolster wear, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with the tactile precision of a brand-new car. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail to document its care. Garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a pristine set of factory floor mats. This isn't just a used car; it's a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
